OL,4,CHalogen lightbulb sales to be banned in
OL,5,CUK under climate change plans
OL,6, Sales of halogen lightbulbs are to be
OL,7, banned in the UK from September, with
OL,8, fluorescent lights to follow, under
OL,9, government climate change plans.
OL,11,FThe move will cut 1.26 million tonnes
OL,12,Fof carbon emissions a year and deliver
OL,13,Fconsumers savings, officials say.
OL,15,FThe UK began phasing out the sale of
OL,16,Fhigher-energy halogen lightbulbs in
OL,17,F2018 under EU-wide rules.
OL,19,FNow retailers will no longer be able to
OL,20,Fsell most remaining halogen bulbs, such
OL,21,Fas kitchen spotlights.
